fields.description:
h3. Steps to Reproduce
Create a new project, follow steps to Run on iOS Device until it asks for a provisioning profile. Select a valid provisioning profile.

h3. Actual Result
Error message 'specified provisioning profile is invalid or is the wrong type'

h3. Expected Result
Provisioning profile to be accepted and app to be compiled and loaded to iOS device
fields.summary: Cannot run on iOS device in Titanium Studio 3

comments.body: This issue is already opened in ticket #TC-1616, sorry I didn't see that one when I opened this.
